sequenceDiagram
    participant B as boot_orchestrator
    participant I as ai_invoker
    participant A as remote_agent
    participant R as code_repair
    participant T as tests
    B->>I: handover(context)
    I->>A: invoke agent
    A-->>I: suggestion
    I->>R: forward suggestion
    R->>T: run tests
    T-->>R: results
    R-->>B: apply & restart
